Purpose: Tokenize a string into a list of tokens
Dependencies: None
Constraints:
- Takes a string as input
- Returns array of tokens
- Each token has type and value fields
- Must handle empty string
- Must handle invalid input
- Must be deterministic
- Must not modify input strings
- Must support standard token types:
  - identifier
  - literal
  - operator
  - delimiter
  - comment
  - whitespace 